{
  "chapter": 54,
  "chapter_summary": "第五十四回《灵犀一点通》讲述胡不愁击败伽星大师后，水天姬擒住企图逃跑的万老夫人。胡不愁展现宽厚胸怀，饶恕万老夫人并带上受伤的伽星大师一同离开海岛。众人发现万老夫人所乘之船被公孙红与梅谦偷走，只得就地取材建造木筏。航行途中伽星大师暗中割断绳索，木筏碎裂，众人落入怒海。水天姬与胡不愁漂流海上，在生死存亡之际互诉衷肠，确认彼此心意。二人几近力竭时发现一艘无人帆船，遂登船求生。本章以二人情感升华为主线，展现绝境中的真情与希望。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_jia_xing_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "伽星大师",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好！好！老僧果然没有白等……紫衣侯的秘笈果然天下无双，竟能使这毛头小子胜过了老僧……",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_bu_chou",
      "speaker_name": "胡不愁",
      "listener": "char_jia_xing_da_shi",
      "text": "只可惜你是瞧不到那秘笈的了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jia_xing_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "伽星大师",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只要这种绝代武功能留传后世，便是武道之幸，便是后人之福，我瞧不瞧得见，又算什么？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "text": "你这老妖精，还想往哪里逃？",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "万老夫人",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "水姑娘，你……你何必又来为难我老婆子？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "text": "为难你？我本该一瞧见你就宰了你才是。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "万老夫人",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "我老婆子对水姑娘一向不错。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "text": "你对我不错？我将你当做知心朋友，你却千方百计地要害死我，这难道也算对我不错？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "万老夫人",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "但……但我老婆子虽然有过，却也有功。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "text": "你还有功？你有什么功？我倒要听听。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "万老夫人",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "若不是我老婆子，胡不……胡大侠此刻只怕还在那密舱中，又怎么会出来，又怎么会击倒伽星大师？",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "text": "你这张嘴呀，果然能将死人都说活！但我可不听你这一套，无论你怎么说，我还是要……",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_bu_chou",
      "speaker_name": "胡不愁",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "你饶了她吧！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_hu_bu_chou",
      "text": "为什么要饶她？这老妖精害的人还不够？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_bu_chou",
      "speaker_name": "胡不愁",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "但她说的本也不错，若不是她这一逼，我当真不知要到何日才敢出来，在那密舱中，我委实已全无自信。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_bu_chou",
      "speaker_name": "胡不愁",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "若不被她这一逼，说不定我永远都不敢出来也未可知。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 73
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_hu_bu_chou",
      "text": "好，你说饶了她，就饶了她，我什么都听你的。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_bu_chou",
      "speaker_name": "胡不愁",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "谢谢你。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_hu_bu_chou",
      "text": "我本该谢谢你才是。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_bu_chou",
      "speaker_name": "胡不愁",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "万老夫人乘来的船，不知还能不能用？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "万老夫人",
      "listener": "char_hu_bu_chou",
      "text": "能用的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "船只要不沉，我就有法子叫它走。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_bu_chou",
      "speaker_name": "胡不愁",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "船上还有人么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "万老夫人",
      "listener": "char_hu_bu_chou",
      "text": "有的，但却已被伽星杀了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_bu_chou",
      "speaker_name": "胡不愁",
      "listener": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "text": "万老夫人，你扶他起来吧！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_hu_bu_chou",
      "text": "扶起他？你要带他走？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_bu_chou",
      "speaker_name": "胡不愁",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "无论如何，此人终究是一代武林宗师，咱们岂能将他弃之于不顾？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_hu_bu_chou",
      "text": "世人皆欲杀，汝意独怜才。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_bu_chou",
      "speaker_name": "胡不愁",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_hu_bu_chou",
      "text": "这么多年来，没有一天我不想赶快离开这鬼地方，但如今真要走，我竟有些舍不得走了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_hu_bu_chou",
      "text": "直到现在，我才发觉这鬼地方竟是如此可爱，假如有一天我能抛开一切住在这里，那我真的什么地方都不想去了。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_bu_chou",
      "speaker_name": "胡不愁",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "只要你真的这么想，那一天总会来的。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_hu_bu_chou",
      "text": "真……真的么？",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_bu_chou",
      "speaker_name": "胡不愁",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "真的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_bu_chou",
      "speaker_name": "胡不愁",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "船在哪里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "万老夫人",
      "listener": "char_hu_bu_chou",
      "text": "明……明是在这里……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "明明是在这里，怎会不见了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "万老夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "奇怪……奇怪……奇怪……奇怪……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_bu_chou",
      "speaker_name": "胡不愁",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "莫非是被浪冲走了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "万老夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不可能，不可能，我明明将船……",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "若不可能被浪冲走，那就是被人驶去了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "万老夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不可能，不可能，公孙红与梅谦明明已死了。",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这也不可能，那也不可能，但船却明明不见了，这究竟是怎么回事？难道撞见了鬼不成？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "万老夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "奇怪……真奇怪……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jia_xing_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "伽星大师",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那两人没有死。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_jia_xing_da_shi",
      "text": "你怎知道？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jia_xing_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "伽星大师",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "是我下的手，我怎会不知。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "万老夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但我明明瞧见……",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jia_xing_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "伽星大师",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "老僧下手，难道还会没有分寸么？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "万老夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "完了……完了……船一定是被那两人偷偷驶走了。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jia_xing_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "伽星大师",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好！好！船走了最好，大家都休想回去。胡不愁呀胡不愁，你七年的苦练就算白费了。",
      "tone": "狂笑",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这里有木头么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_bu_chou",
      "speaker_name": "胡不愁",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "自然有的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_hu_bu_chou",
      "text": "只要有木头，咱们就能回去。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "万老夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，不错，以我老婆子的经验，这几天决不会有暴风雨，水姑娘和胡大侠都已时来运转了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "text": "你倒是善颂善祷。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_bu_chou",
      "speaker_name": "胡不愁",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "七年……故人别来不知是否无恙？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_hu_bu_chou",
      "text": "你还多想什么，反正就快见着他们了。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_bu_chou",
      "speaker_name": "胡不愁",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "我已等了七年，不知怎的，这几天反似等不得了。我那莫大哥、金二哥……唉！他们现在想必已声名大起。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 265
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_hu_bu_chou",
      "text": "凭他们的本事，想不成名都不可能。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_bu_chou",
      "speaker_name": "胡不愁",
      "listener": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "text": "正是如此……万老夫人，你可知道他们近来的消息？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "万老夫人",
      "listener": "char_hu_bu_chou",
      "text": "我……我不太清楚。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_hu_bu_chou",
      "text": "同样的话，你已不知问过多少次了，她也不知已回答过多少次，现在你还要问个什么？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_bu_chou",
      "speaker_name": "胡不愁",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我总是有些不放心……我总是有些不信。万老夫人在江湖中可说是万事通了，又怎会不知道他们的消息？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_hu_bu_chou",
      "text": "万事通总也有不知道的事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "万老夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "正是，正是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_bu_chou",
      "speaker_name": "胡不愁",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "还有宝儿，这孩子想必已长大了。以他的聪明，我深信他必能成名，只是，却猜不到他已长成什么模样？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 291
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_hu_bu_chou",
      "text": "这句话你也……",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_bu_chou",
      "speaker_name": "胡不愁",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "我知道这句话我也不知说过多少次了，但我只要一想起他以前那种调皮捣蛋的样子，就又忍不住要重说一次。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_hu_bu_chou",
      "text": "你如此想他们，却不知他们是否在想你？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_bu_chou",
      "speaker_name": "胡不愁",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "自然也想的……就算不想，我也要想他们。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_hu_bu_chou",
      "text": "但人家若不想我，我就决不去想他们。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_bu_chou",
      "speaker_name": "胡不愁",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "这就是你和我的不同，你……",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_jia_xing_da_shi",
      "text": "你笑什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jia_xing_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "伽星大师",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我笑你们都是在痴人说梦。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_jia_xing_da_shi",
      "text": "你才胡说八道，我们……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jia_xing_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "伽星大师",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们再也休想见着他们了，你们再也休想回去。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "万老夫人",
      "listener": "char_jia_xing_da_shi",
      "text": "你……你说什么？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jia_xing_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "伽星大师",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这只木筏立刻就要沉了。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_jia_xing_da_shi",
      "text": "你……你放屁！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jia_xing_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "伽星大师",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "绳子立刻就要断了。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_bu_chou",
      "speaker_name": "胡不愁",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这是怎么回事？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 331
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jia_xing_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "伽星大师",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这自然是老僧动的手脚。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_jia_xing_da_shi",
      "text": "你疯了？你难道也不要命了？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jia_xing_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "伽星大师",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "老僧正是已不要命。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "万老夫人",
      "listener": "char_jia_xing_da_shi",
      "text": "你可是生怕我不给你解药，所以才如此？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jia_xing_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "伽星大师",
      "listener": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "text": "哼！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "万老夫人",
      "listener": "char_jia_xing_da_shi",
      "text": "但我那是骗你的，那梅子里根本没有毒。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jia_xing_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "伽星大师",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有毒无毒，俱都无妨。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "万老夫人",
      "listener": "char_jia_xing_da_shi",
      "text": "那……那你又是为了什么？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jia_xing_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "伽星大师",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "老僧既不能得到此物，便要它陪老僧同沉海底。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "万老夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你疯了……你疯了……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_bu_chou",
      "speaker_name": "胡不愁",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "大家且莫惊慌，先镇定下来，再作……",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jia_xing_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "伽星大师",
      "listener": "char_hu_bu_chou",
      "text": "胡不愁呀胡不愁，你镇定又有何用？你学会了紫衣侯的武功又有何用？还是随老僧一起去海底躺着吧！",
      "tone": "狂笑",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 362
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_hu_bu_chou",
      "text": "胡不愁……",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "水天姬……",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_hu_bu_chou",
      "text": "胡不愁……胡不愁……你在哪里？",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 400,
      "line_end": 402
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_bu_chou",
      "speaker_name": "胡不愁",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "醒醒，醒醒，我在这里……",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 408,
      "line_end": 408
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_hu_bu_chou",
      "text": "你不要走……你永远再也莫要离开我……",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 412,
      "line_end": 412
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_hu_bu_chou",
      "text": "万老夫人呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 428,
      "line_end": 428
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_bu_chou",
      "speaker_name": "胡不愁",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "不知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 430,
      "line_end": 430
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_hu_bu_chou",
      "text": "伽星……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 432,
      "line_end": 432
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_bu_chou",
      "speaker_name": "胡不愁",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "不知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 434,
      "line_end": 434
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_hu_bu_chou",
      "text": "看来只有我们两人还活着。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 436,
      "line_end": 436
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_bu_chou",
      "speaker_name": "胡不愁",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 438,
      "line_end": 438
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_hu_bu_chou",
      "text": "只要我们还活着，就能回去。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 440,
      "line_end": 440
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_bu_chou",
      "speaker_name": "胡不愁",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "不错，我们一定能回去。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 442,
      "line_end": 442
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_hu_bu_chou",
      "text": "我们不久就会见到你想见的那些人了，莫不屈、金不畏、公孙不智，还有方宝儿……是么？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 444,
      "line_end": 446
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_bu_chou",
      "speaker_name": "胡不愁",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "还有我的师父，你的母亲……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 448,
      "line_end": 448
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_hu_bu_chou",
      "text": "我们不久就能喝到甜甜的水，那比海水要甜得多……还有舒服的床、新鲜的水果……是么？",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 450,
      "line_end": 452
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_bu_chou",
      "speaker_name": "胡不愁",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "你想吃什么就有什么。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 454,
      "line_end": 454
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_hu_bu_chou",
      "text": "我想吃水蜜桃、大白梨，还有西瓜，又甜又大的西瓜……",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 456,
      "line_end": 456
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_hu_bu_chou",
      "text": "我们何苦还在自己骗自己！你知道，我也知道，我们是再也不能回去了，什么人我们都已见不着。",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 458,
      "line_end": 462
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_bu_chou",
      "speaker_name": "胡不愁",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "莫哭……莫要哭……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 464,
      "line_end": 464
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_hu_bu_chou",
      "text": "你可知道，我自从长大后，就只有笑，就只有瞧别人哭，自己从未哭过，但今天，我……我竟哭了两次。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 470,
      "line_end": 472
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_bu_chou",
      "speaker_name": "胡不愁",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "你……我……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 474,
      "line_end": 474
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_hu_bu_chou",
      "text": "其实我不该哭的，我本该笑的……有你在旁边陪着我，我还有什么遗憾？我还要再求什么？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 476,
      "line_end": 478
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_bu_chou",
      "speaker_name": "胡不愁",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "想不到……想不到你会对我……",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 482,
      "line_end": 482
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_hu_bu_chou",
      "text": "我也想不到我会对你这样……这是缘，不是么？若不是这许许多多的灾难，我又怎会和你在一起？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 484,
      "line_end": 486
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_bu_chou",
      "speaker_name": "胡不愁",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "灾难……许许多多的灾难……我该恨还是该感激？",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 488,
      "line_end": 488
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_hu_bu_chou",
      "text": "我要感激的。若不是如此，我只怕永远也不知道我也有真实的情感……有了真情，死又算什么？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 490,
      "line_end": 492
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_hu_bu_chou",
      "text": "亲爱的……永别了！",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 510,
      "line_end": 512
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_bu_chou",
      "speaker_name": "胡不愁",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "你说什么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 514,
      "line_end": 514
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_hu_bu_chou",
      "text": "我已受不住了，要……要先去了。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 516,
      "line_end": 516
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_bu_chou",
      "speaker_name": "胡不愁",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "你……你不能。",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 518,
      "line_end": 518
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_hu_bu_chou",
      "text": "再挣扎下去，也不过是多受苦而已，你……你还是让我早些走吧。你难道情愿让我多受苦么？",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 520,
      "line_end": 522
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_bu_chou",
      "speaker_name": "胡不愁",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "但你……你……",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 524,
      "line_end": 524
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_hu_bu_chou",
      "text": "让我走吧，求求你，让我走吧！",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 528,
      "line_end": 528
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_bu_chou",
      "speaker_name": "胡不愁",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "若是要走，咱们就一起走。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 530,
      "line_end": 530
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_hu_bu_chou",
      "text": "你不能，你不能……你还有机会。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 532,
      "line_end": 532
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_bu_chou",
      "speaker_name": "胡不愁",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "你走了，我还有什么机会？你难道还不知道这许多年来我是凭着什么支持下去的？能够和你在一起死，我已觉得心满意足，你……",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 534,
      "line_end": 536
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_bu_chou",
      "speaker_name": "胡不愁",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "啊，你不必死了，我也不必死了！你瞧，那是什么？",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 538,
      "line_end": 540
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_bu_chou",
      "speaker_name": "胡不愁",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "船上的朋友，能不能把船驶过来，救我们一命。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 550,
      "line_end": 551
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_bu_chou",
      "speaker_name": "胡不愁",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "船上的朋友，可听见我的话么？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 554,
      "line_end": 554
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_hu_bu_chou",
      "text": "船上像是没有人？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 560,
      "line_end": 560
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_bu_chou",
      "speaker_name": "胡不愁",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "奇怪，的确有些奇怪。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 562,
      "line_end": 562
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_hu_bu_chou",
      "text": "这艘船莫非已被海盗洗劫，船上的人已死光了？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 564,
      "line_end": 564
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_bu_chou",
      "speaker_name": "胡不愁",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "无论如何，咱们先设法上船再说。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 566,
      "line_end": 566
    }
